<p>This application is designed to manage Products and Categories using ASP.NET Core MVC with N-Tier Architecture.</p>

<ul>
    <li><strong>Technologies Used:</strong> ASP.NET Core, Entity Framework Core, Dependency Injection, Repository & Unit of Work Pattern.</li>
    <li>
        <strong>Features:</strong>
        <ul>
            <li>Create, Read, Update, Delete (CRUD) operations for Products and Categories.</li>
            <li>Separation of concerns using N-Tier Architecture.</li>
            <li>Dynamic Views with proper data binding and validation.</li>
        </ul>
    </li>
</ul>
